snippet.title: Go To Our Room When I Have Company
snippet.description: Welcome back to She & I Podcast. This week B~Love and India Marie give a brief Thanksgiving recap following that up with India Marie’s Pilates schedule. B~Love then asked India Marie if she feels obligated to leave the room when he has company. Then he tells a story about changing a car tire and battery. In B~Love’s relationTIP, he talks about Christmas lists and being surprised when you get what you asked for. While, in WWID, India Marie answers a listener letter about the preferred sex of a child.
